

IS A - Relationship depends on inheritance;

For example a Potato is a Vegetable.
A Car is vehicle.



HAS A- Relationship is known as composition.
it is also used for code reUsability in java.

it simply means Instance of one class has reference to the instance of another class.
 -> Car has a engine.



    Java beans is an example of encapsulation.


     Can we inherit final method/inherit static method?
         Factory method

         ------------

         Composition
         Car has a Engine object
         Strong relationship
         both classes are not  independent of each other.

         --------
         Aggregation is weak relationship
         team and players
         a player can exist without the team

